{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Zombies are around us!</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Around Us : Zombie Shooter is a multiplayer cooperative zombie shooting game. There are various kinds of zombies and bosses. You goal is to survive through waves of zombies. Get upgrade and go to the highest wave that no one ever reaches! .... and you will see why amount matters.... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/zombies.gif?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Let's survive together</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can play together upto 6 players with combination of local and online multiplayer. 1 keyboard can play 2 players, connect game controller to add more, let other online player join to add more. You, your partner and your online friends can now play together! Isn't that awesome? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Also, this game is cross platform multiplayer currently available on PC and mobile (Android). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Awesome weapons</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Satisfy experience of popping zombies using weapons that unlock along your journey. Each weapon is unique, and you! Yes, you. You also unique, find your right ones. I'm sure you'll love them. These are some of our awesome newly updated weapons:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/shopItems.png?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/ezgif-7-5bf30af56c.gif?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Have fun with roguelite upgrade style</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With each wave, the zombie horde grows stronger, and just weapons won\u2019t be enough. Thankfully, you\u2019ll have access to an upgrade system, both in-match and off-match. Discover random upgrades, unlock new abilities, and experiment to find your ultimate \u2018cheat\u2019 build. It's time for HERO!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/charge_gun_demo.gif?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Over 30 Zombie types</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle over 30 unique zombie types like Jumpers, Spikes, Invisibles, and Bombers. With intense boss fights along the way, every encounter will push your survival skills to the limit!&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/sharkGif.gif?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Map &amp; Challenges</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore 4 unique maps, each packed with 9 challenges. Conquer different terrains and face a variety of intense challenges as you fight to survive the undead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Future plan</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our goal is to make the game that you, your family members and friends can play together with no limit. You can use what ever device you like to play, spent the day together fighting over 100 waves of zombies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/AllZombie_small.png?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Involve with our development</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We hear you. Tell us what you think. Your valuable feedbacks will be on out mind. So feel free to join our community platform or contact us. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/thanks_image.png?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can get our latest news on Facebook or join us on Discord. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And be sure to <strong>add AroundUs to your game wishlist.</strong></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First zombie","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2437950/2c27401210a81e6aa35d56b798abb46e507d284a.jpg"},{"name":"Roulette?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2437950/1d151004c60aaf423ea6bb9035eb9e8203ebe2fe.jpg"},{"name":"Speed god","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2437950/8d44b06445da55557e627186a99ad9c748eda000.jpg"},{"name":"Tanker","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2437950/c3545fde36d432e9db7cb40e2b630764b2345869.jpg"},{"name":"Powerful weapon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2437950/b39ba73fe6629ec5c79109525fdd6658988d4f4c.jpg"},{"name":"Ability stone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2437950/498890685c9e7d79fa6bcb5607424069377da802.jpg"},{"name":"True Super card","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2437950/5810cba3869ccd4bec9d288c1ef61a9b00bfa20b.jpg"},{"name":"First try","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2437950/3b8d687f7db26188cd2ba6d508b67f5f04811eb0.jpg"},{"name":"New gun","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2437950/9ca019ce2bd396a2e5fed87fd82c789b3015caf5.jpg"},{"name":"First time to heaven","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2437950/05f7dad21af59851249287d4817b362bab93ade0.jpg"}],"total":69},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2437950?t=1730525792","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2437950?t=1730525792","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/c77e3c5472a906b921218d9cf7e50de69cbd921a/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730525792","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/c77e3c5472a906b921218d9cf7e50de69cbd921a/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730525792","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Stats","id":15},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2459040,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Zombies are around us!</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Around Us : Zombie Shooter is a multiplayer cooperative zombie shooting game. There are various kinds of zombies and bosses. You goal is to survive through waves of zombies. Get upgrade and go to the highest wave that no one ever reaches! .... and you will see why amount matters.... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/zombies.gif?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Let's survive together</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can play together upto 6 players with combination of local and online multiplayer. 1 keyboard can play 2 players, connect game controller to add more, let other online player join to add more. You, your partner and your online friends can now play together! Isn't that awesome? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Also, this game is cross platform multiplayer currently available on PC and mobile (Android). </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Awesome weapons</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Satisfy experience of popping zombies using weapons that unlock along your journey. Each weapon is unique, and you! Yes, you. You also unique, find your right ones. I'm sure you'll love them. These are some of our awesome newly updated weapons:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/shopItems.png?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/ezgif-7-5bf30af56c.gif?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Have fun with roguelite upgrade style</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With each wave, the zombie horde grows stronger, and just weapons won\u2019t be enough. Thankfully, you\u2019ll have access to an upgrade system, both in-match and off-match. Discover random upgrades, unlock new abilities, and experiment to find your ultimate \u2018cheat\u2019 build. It's time for HERO!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/charge_gun_demo.gif?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Over 30 Zombie types</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle over 30 unique zombie types like Jumpers, Spikes, Invisibles, and Bombers. With intense boss fights along the way, every encounter will push your survival skills to the limit!&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/sharkGif.gif?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Map &amp; Challenges</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore 4 unique maps, each packed with 9 challenges. Conquer different terrains and face a variety of intense challenges as you fight to survive the undead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Future plan</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our goal is to make the game that you, your family members and friends can play together with no limit. You can use what ever device you like to play, spent the day together fighting over 100 waves of zombies. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/AllZombie_small.png?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Involve with our development</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We hear you. Tell us what you think. Your valuable feedbacks will be on out mind. So feel free to join our community platform or contact us. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/extras/thanks_image.png?t=1730525792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can get our latest news on Facebook or join us on Discord. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And be sure to <strong>add AroundUs to your game wishlist.</strong></p>","developers":["Burapa Phatichon"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Early Access","id":"70"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2437950/header.jpg?t=1730525792","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257042296,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.s